Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:03.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:07.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make sure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:13.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:18.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guild was attacked by the official guild Phantom Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:22.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail has never gotten along well with them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They beat up Levy's team and kidnapped Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:29.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So an all-out confrontation began!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for even more who-knows-what!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:41.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to mystery is right in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:44.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world's a wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:47.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,which we're already wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:52.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This excitement gets my heart racing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:59.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What is real, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I see tomorrow, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:10.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The only part leveling up is my curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:15.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just throw away our daily life together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:23.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! S. O. W.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:29.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Living itself will be our training!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:32.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for even more who-knows-what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:40.82,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be satisfied with just the normal answers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This magical wonder life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:46.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Our future is wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:51.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best living our life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the way we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:56.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy Heatfilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Card Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lighting, Reverse Tower, Lovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jolt of Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:00.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Twister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:11.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man, then you're a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Take Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His arm's Taken Over by a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who absorbs the power of monsters he defeats into his arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Arm Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:32.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:34.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Iron Dragon Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hurt Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nab!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He even took out his own guildmates in that hit! {The previous wording and the vague visuals made it seem like Nab was Gajeel's ally.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:59.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Iron Dragon Slayer, Gajeel the Great, will face you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm trash, but I'm a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:19.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man must be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him... His own comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're lookin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel was blown backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:41.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen that before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:47.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fairy Tail's Dragon Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman, give this guy to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:55.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... Not only do you use me as a floor mat, {I think of footstools as things for resting on rather than stepping on}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you plan on interfering in our Man-on-Man battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pillar of the Iron Dragon! {Pillar, maybe? I forget how I translated it... (He didn't use the word in this scene)}{Translation of "kon" is tricky... it was not in most of my dictionaries but I found it in the full kanji dictionary.  It means the obvious thing: a long, round cylinder...  Pole seems kind of lame though...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy busted up the guild and hurt Levy and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:13.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, they're havin' fun, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:25.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice being young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:31.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! I'll let you have that manly battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'll knock him good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:40.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't affect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:51.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:56.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, bring it. You're not affected either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know me pretty good there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one hot and uncomfortable guy, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:10.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you hard-ass. {Nice!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:20.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get ahead of yourself, you scrap-iron bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:25.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Just as the rumors say... That's some decent power you got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:26.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouchy, ouchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:30.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Is that all you got, Salamander?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This was just a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before our Dragon's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a bit of a destructive streak in you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:17.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's master Makarov's anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant's Wrath...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire guild is shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Man, Master Makarov!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:39.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourselves! As long as our master is here, we cannot lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:10.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while, Makarov-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:17.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not since the regular meeting six years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I made a fool of myself then. {I interpreted it as himself (from the mairu meaning "I lost" in a general sort of way}{is the subject him or Makarov?  usually "mairu" would be used for the person being spoken to}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Liquor really does me in. {He's buying time until Aria can get set up. So he doesn't care if the story reflect badly on himself} {I think this is the implication.  At least recalling what Makarov did at the last meeting}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:34.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not come here to chat, Jose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a thought-projection?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:42.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! You ran from the guild? {"escape" has the nuance of getting out of a tough spot (positive) rather than running scared, like Makarov is implying}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:48.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A battle between two of the 10 Great Wizard Saints would surely cause a cataclysm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:54.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would prefer a simple, sensible victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and fight me fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she's part of your own guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:16.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you have no idea who Lucy Heartfilia-sama is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I never sensed this guy's presence! {"couldn't" in this instance has a bunch of interpretations}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The, the, the sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something fell down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sadness is too great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does this sadness come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:51.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the sadness of a great wizard disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My power... I've lost my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:09:59.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:09:59.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:00.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:04.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:08.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the magic of one of the Element 4, Aria-san of the Heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can empty his opponent of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:15.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, his magic is to "nullify."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:20.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle is already mine, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:31.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My magical power..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magical power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:34.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:35.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world? I can't sense any magical power at all from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:43.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean he's now nothing but a little old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is boring. And right when things were heating up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:55.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it... How did they beat Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do they have up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their master's been beaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:02.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're at less than half strength now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:10.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we've still got Gajeel and the Element 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance! Crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky! {How about a good old Star Wars' "Don't get cocky!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, they've...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:24.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...gotten their fighting spirit back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:28.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Triple Element Combination Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! {"Shoot" sounds like an obvious swearing censorship to the hard-core fans.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:36.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta do better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Don't force yourself at your age!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:41.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me old!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see where this is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. It's not just about attacking strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:56.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our moral is critically low as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:58.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone return to the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:04.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man does not withdraw! {Yes, it's better}{okay, maybe "withdraw" would be better :) }
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can fight as well, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Without the master, we cannot defeat Jose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:14.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:22.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Already running with your tails between your legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:25.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You never had the guts, you Fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:27.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreats are sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All too sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aria? You're always creeping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:36.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, good job getting the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all Master Jose's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry at every little thing! You're annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did they catch Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl named Lucy is being held in our headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:56.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So we gave her a "warm welcome," then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:05.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finish this one day, Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:11.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They caught Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:17.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd retreat now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to get revenge for Levy's team!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:22.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:24.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:31.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do now... is pull back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hole the master left is too great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:51.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Salamander... and a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:54.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You and me are gonna talk! {Tsura wo kasu is a rude idiom. It's a way to say I want to talk to you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:08.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save Lucy, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:14.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-How would I know? Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot! It's hot! I'm burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:23.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know nothin', seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If any more of my friends are hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:33.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be nothing but a pile of ashes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:37.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never heard of the wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I don't know about the young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:42.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that so? Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to make charcoal, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:49.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But our headquarters is up ahead. She may be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that in the first place, sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:52.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is... Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awake, are we? Lucy Heatfilia-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:22.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the guild master of Phantom Lord, Jose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:24.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I was captured by the Element 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:35.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that this filthy cell and shackles are quite rude of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but you are you currently a prisoner, so I hope you understand the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Remove these at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:46.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prisoner? How dare you do that to Levy-chan's team!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:54.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone of your status, I have prepared accommodations for a welcomed guest instead of a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ew, ew, ew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:02.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You don't want to stay in this cell, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:07.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cooperate, I'll transfer you to the suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you attack us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:11.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:13.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you referring to Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:18.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in passing... A side effect. {"In passing" has a vague meaning, so maybe we should have the repitition identify the meaning a little}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:25.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our true objective was to obtain a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:31.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that someone just happened to be in Fairy Tail, so we crushed it on our way... That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:39.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're much denser than I figured the daughter of the Heartfilia family would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:47.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Daughter of the Heartfilia Konzern, Mistress Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:55.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you hid this fact from the people of the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:58.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the daughter of one of the wealthiest families in the country
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:03.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,take on such cheap, dangerous jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:05.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a kidnapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:12.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were requested to bring you back with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:16.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By none other than your father himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:28.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's because he wanted to search for his beloved daughter who ran away from home. {In this case, kawaii means to dote on. Beloved seems to sum that up in one word}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the kind of person that'd care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:38.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going back, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:40.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going back to that house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... What a troublesome little lady we have ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Release me this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:48.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:49.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda need to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:57.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's this? That's the oldest trick in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:03.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:05.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of ways to deal with that old trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:14.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A bucket, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such an improper lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am a gentleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:32.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best not to underestimate the old tricks! {"suteru mono ja nai" is an idiomatic phrase}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:49.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sky cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did me a good one there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to punish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must show you how scary Phantom can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:32.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard his voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here, I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:38.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucys are falling from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:06.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nuts, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:11.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... I thought you were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:20.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. Let's go back to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? This is the headquarters... We should- {one dash? M-dashes are usually noted in ascii by two dashes}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:30.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Erza said to retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:34.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't afraid of them at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:36.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master's been severely wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:38.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay 'em back for that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't handle it by yourself, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:41.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:44.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:45.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nab broke his arm... {you'll see in the next episode it's his arm}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:49.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Macao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:52.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause he's an old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:53.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:56.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:19.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all... This is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:25.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I still want to be in the guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:29.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:36.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:48.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you can be in the guild. What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:51.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:53.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, come on, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll carry you on my back, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:06.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're making Natsu cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:08.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've gone and done it, girly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:27.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:30.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:40.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chasing after your profile left only in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:52.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "I never want to see your face again," when you left me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:57.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But the tears on your cheek said it all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:03.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time you felt like you'd be swallowed up in the waves of contradiction
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:10.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,you always held back your tears, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:21.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"What a strong person," they said, but everyone overestimated you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:30.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and before you knew it you lost sight of who you really are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:34.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the sun I thought would always be near me collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:37.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and the light shut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:41.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbing out the truths and the lies of one day, altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:42.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:45.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:54.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,still, ironically, chasing after your profile in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.49,0:24:01.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's late. It's way past the time we were going to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:02.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Happy, early are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.95,0:24:06.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're late, Natsu! What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:11.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But my stomach told me this was just about the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell time by your stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: 15 Minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty peaked, let's get something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.64,0:24:20.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about my shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish are on sale today...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.99,0:24:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where, where, where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:26.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
